![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/0dc64db2-e817-4c41-81b8-26fd2fed85c9/14606.jpg?format=original)

John Cena and Logan Paul open up Smackdown with a back and forth that saw Logan Paul insulting the crowd IN FRENCH.

John Cena calls Logan Paul stupid for thinking he can become a real WWE Superstar without the support of the fans. John Cena sees potential in Logan Paul.

Cena says this is a teachable moment so he finds the kid he insulted in the crowd earlier this year apologized to him. Kid was more worried about his selfie than the moment but he figured it out in the end.

Logan Paul says wrap this charity case stuff up. Cena says "You're the one who wanted the match, Dickhead."

Cena leaves the promo saying Logan Paul is going up against the greatest so he better be ready

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/280238b2-bd6a-4af4-b2f5-9d543e34a311/14602.jpg?format=original)

