*   ## **_ALEXA BLISS DEF. CHELSEA GREEN_**
    

Chelsea and Alba Fyre attacked Charlotte and Bliss before their Tag Team match, injuring Charlotte and screwing themselves out of a title match.

Post match, Bliss is jumped by Green and Fyre. Charlotte runs out to save her but it isn't enough. Fyre and Green stand tall.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ebdc27ee-b786-4873-9fac-4837ec3b8f5f/14613.jpg?format=original)

Cathy Kelly interviews Damian Priest who says Aleister Black doesn't know what he's getting himself into. But he's about to find out.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8b8e5c93-1c2d-4389-8d70-bc70db4df832/14619.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_MICHIN DEF. KIANA JAMES IN TEN SECONDS_**
    

Post match Giulia and Kiana beat Michin down.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3a610c30-015f-4997-b3ca-214f5aafbe67/14626.jpg?format=original)

Drew McIntyre calls out Randy Orton. Orton comes out to a massive ovation. Drew says if Orton attacked him to get revenge for losing at Summerslam then that's cool.

But if Orton attacked Drew for Cody Rhodes then Orton is wrong. Cody is not a friend. If Cody called up Orton in the hospital it wasn't to check up, it was to get info.

Orton says he actually understands and he will take note of that. But he didn't attack for Cody. He attacked Drew because he thinks Drew is a prick. A brawl begins. Orton is going to Punt kick Drew when security runs down.

RKOs for everyone including agent Hurricane Helms!!

