![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9efb7856-40d6-426a-afc0-0725cc183690/14637.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_WWE US CHAMPIONSHIP: Sami Zayn def. Solo Sikoa(c)_**
    

Sami Zayn is the new United States Champion after a match with Solo Sikoa that saw the NFTs interfering and the Bloodline’s Jimmy Uso and Jacob Fatu coming out to even the odds.

In the end, Sami Zayn pins Solo after two Helluva kicks to win his first US Title